                     <interp inst="t18351026-2244-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="stealingFromMaster"></interp>for stealing, on the <rs id="t18351026-cd-109" type="crimeDate">
                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18351026-2244-offence-1 t18351026-cd-109"></join>22nd of October</rs>, 2 handkerchiefs, value 3<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; 1 milk-jug, value 3<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.; 1 smell<lb></lb>ing-bottle, value 1<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; 11b. of soap, value 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.; 1 bottle, value 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.; and one pint and a half of wine, value 2<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; the goods of <persName id="t18351026-name-751" type="victimName">
